fields.name: Effect:
fields.value:
Put 2 players into a Duel with each other. Whoever earns more card points at the end of the duel wins the duel and gets to gain a card of their choice. Whoever loses the duel takes 2 HP of unblockable damage.

*Check Dueling for information about Duels. Check <#1191650444594909354> for information on card points.*
